_sText:
**I present to you! My third map "Aim_Depot"!**

It's been forever since I've uploaded my second map "[Awp_dustwars](http://css.gamebanana.com/maps/170176 "awp_dustwars")",
so I decided to open Hammer Editor and start on something.. AND BAM, this map was created.

The map is a depot/storage area.
The map contains alot of cover and some nice spots for gunfights. The map is fairly balanced. The map has a dust theme.
_Feedback is always welcome._
